text: Jean-Paul Lecoq (born October 13, 1958 in Le Havre) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Seine-Maritime department, and is a member of the French Communist Party. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:People from Le Havre Category:Mayors of places in Normandy Category:French Communist Party politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
